{
  "3116120": {
    "name": "兽人领地",
    "steam_appid": 3116120,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116120/extras/2f4c7097c039cdff30dec9d29d8e29a9.avif?t=1763545306\" width=600 height=90 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中，你可以在任意位置摆放防御塔，但该如何摆放防御塔才能收益最大化？到底应该先放采集塔攒钱还是先放防御塔攻击敌人解决目前难题？什么时机释放法术等等，都需要考虑进去，迎接每一波到来的兽潮！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏的防御塔摆放还是基于物理规则，你可以通过摆放一个新的防御塔推动来修正上一个防御塔的位置错误，根据战局随时调整你的策略。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116120/extras/96778b9fa56568a34961986ee5d0c89a.poster.avif?t=1763545306\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116120/extras/96778b9fa56568a34961986ee5d0c89a.webm?t=1763545306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116120/extras/96778b9fa56568a34961986ee5d0c89a.mp4?t=1763545306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116120/extras/75b8b441b988b2832da79f416c0c2a6f.avif?t=1763545306\" width=600 height=90 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏共有5个大地图，每个地图都是不一样的地图环境，并且都有不一样的效果特性。比如冰雪地图，玩家必须建造篝火，否则温暖区外的建筑将进入冰冻状态，攻击和采集速度下降。沙漠地图则会让防御塔相邻升温，达到3级升温后攻击速度会加快，但同时受到的伤害也会增加，风险与收益并存。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏每个地图都会有不同的兽人敌军，惧怕火焰但数量庞大的幼狼群、超远程攻击的投矛兽人等等，游戏中每个地图还有许多有趣的设计等待你来挖掘！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116120/extras/368d9a737d1c33993aa38239d9a3500f.poster.avif?t=1763545306\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116120/extras/368d9a737d1c33993aa38239d9a3500f.webm?t=1763545306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116120/extras/368d9a737d1c33993aa38239d9a3500f.mp4?t=1763545306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116120/extras/a918f5cfeca80203ac29fa32f31c4c2b.avif?t=1763545306\" width=600 height=90 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中拥有数十种防御塔，有克制各种各样敌人的防御塔，比如迫击炮可以范围攻击敌人、魔能塔可以发射激光射线、捕获塔能有效对空中敌人造成伤害等等。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了防御塔，玩家也能装备法术卷轴，一次性释放能造成大量伤害或效果，火球术能够瞬间秒杀兽人小兵，迷雾术能够大片降低远程敌人的攻击距离等等，多种搭配组合让游戏的通关方式不止一种。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116120/extras/edef5e821b85c2abc09681aa15be22eb.poster.avif?t=1763545306\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116120/extras/edef5e821b85c2abc09681aa15be22eb.webm?t=1763545306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116120/extras/edef5e821b85c2abc09681aa15be22eb.mp4?t=1763545306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116120/extras/b39de6f5f6e0702261c6c616f87a2303.avif?t=1763545306\" width=600 height=90 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏除了需要在恰当时机摆放防御塔和释放法术，还需要在面临四面八方兽潮的同时攻击各种中立建筑，有些中立建筑能为你提供改变战局的正向BUFF，比如获得法术卷轴，有些则是有效阻止敌人的进攻，比如摧毁传送门后，最后一波兽潮敌人才不会额外召唤。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116120/extras/7d0cc84b2e5d636e813f324aba593720.poster.avif?t=1763545306\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116120/extras/7d0cc84b2e5d636e813f324aba593720.webm?t=1763545306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116120/extras/7d0cc84b2e5d636e813f324aba593720.mp4?t=1763545306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏每个关卡提供了3种难度供大家自由选择，还有挑战玩法可以体验，休闲或烧脑可自由选择！游戏还有趣味性十足的娱乐关卡，暴风雪关卡每隔一段时间会让全体兽人冰冻，流沙模式会让防御塔慢慢往外移动等等，各种脑洞大开的关卡等你来体验！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116120/extras/0eb9816e10ee9a5aec0d4a51f2d9eec2.poster.avif?t=1763545306\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116120/extras/0eb9816e10ee9a5aec0d4a51f2d9eec2.webm?t=1763545306\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3116120/extras/0eb9816e10ee9a5aec0d4a51f2d9eec2.mp4?t=1763545306\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
